{
  "stem": "159.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were-- had to stay on our knees all night long because we did not wear that armband.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was so scared and crying all night long.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the next morning, they let us go home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was my first experience with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What followed?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the end of '39 because they came in September to Bedzin, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After this, we couldn't go to school anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to have a certain time that we cannot go out at night anymore.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And times were very bad with food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I couldn't see my friends, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were just like-- everybody was cooped up in the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And 1942 in December, they knocked on our door in the middle of the night, and they had to have a certain amount of girls to take to camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they knocked on my door, and they wanted me to go with them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I'll never forget this that my father was crying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[SOBBING] He wanted to give them money to leave me home, but they wouldn't listen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They just took me away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was-- and since they send me to camp that time, my three brothers were left with my parents that time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the ghetto happened after, not at my time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I think the ghetto occurred in end of 19-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] 1939, '43, I think.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They just need a certain amount of girls to go and work at camps, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's why they're rounding up one time, girls, one time, boys, one time, men.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had certain orders to do what to round up and when.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's how it was going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They sent me to next town's [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They sent me.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
